                	<h3>Portfolio</h3><hr /><br>
                    <p><h5>East Town<br />(Kanchpur/Madanpur)</h5>
                        <img src="./images/east-town.jpg"/>
                        East Town Project has come up on the Dhaka-Chittagong highway just adjacent to the Kanchpur Bridge at Madanpur in a crowd free environment.   300 ft wide under construction Dhaka eastern (by-pass) highway which has passed along its side will be providing additional facilities to this project. There will be a most modern shopping complex along with all kinds of facilities of city life in this project.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <br />
                    <p><h5>West Town<br />(Hemayetpur/Dhalla)</h5> <img src="./images/west-town.jpg"/>Just at a near distance from Sangshad Bhaban, the West Town Project is situated by the side of Dhaka-Savar highway on the river Dhaleswari only 25 minutes drive from sangshad Bhaban. You can develop a safe and attractive living place for your next generation in this project.</p>
                    <br>
                    <br />
                    <p><h5>North Town<br />(Tongi/Gutia)</h5> <img src="./images/north-town.jpg"/>North Town Project, with its own glamour situated on the river Turag under Tongi Pourashava neighboured with the International Medical College and Hospital, Government and Non-government Schools and Colleges and many other city life facilities.</p>
                    <br>
                    <br />
                    <p><h5>South Town<br />(Keraniganj/Baghair)</h5> <img src="./images/south-town.jpg"/>As you cross the Buriganga Bridge 1&2, beside 300 ft wide Dhaka-Maowa highway South Town Project will attract you where you may find an excellent pollution free environment along with all city life facilities. In the recent past Bashundhara Riverview Project, Jhilmil Project of RAJUK and Armed Forces DOHS Project have come up in this part of the mega city to develop a greater Residential Area.</p>
                    <br>
                    <br />
                    <p><h5>New Town<br />(Sonargoan/Meghnaghat)</h5> <img src="./images/new-town.jpg"/>New Town Project has come into reality on the bank of the River Meghna blended with spelendid natural beauty in Sonargoan, a rich locality of rare stock of Bengal's historical relics & folk traditions. There are latest shopping centres, banks, community centres, post office, clinics and beautiful mosque along with many other city life facilities located in this place.</p>
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    <p><h5>SAARC</h5> <img src="./images/SAARC.jpg"/>The SAARC INDUSTRIAL ESTATE is established with the idea of relieving all those troubles and bottlenecks by developing a favourable atmosphere for the prospective entrepreneurs.</p>
                    <br>
                    <br />
                    <p><h5>Shyamoli Plaza</h5> <img src="./images/shamoli.jpg"/>Shyamoli Plaza is one of our superb apartment projects at Shyamoli, prime location of Dhaka city. Schools, Colleges, Hospitals, Bazar, Park, and different Govt. Offices even the Shangshad Bhaban are within walking distance from the project.</p>
                    <br>
                    <br />
                    <p><h5>Nakshi Kantha</h5> <img src="./images/nakshi.jpg"/>Named after a traditional craft of Bangladesh, the Nakshi Kantha (which is a hand-embroidered quilt usually made by rural women)  is located at Kabi Jasimuddin Road next to Motijheel Commercial Area, the business centre of the capital city.</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>The project comprises of a twin tower of 12 storied buildings. Special emphasis has been given to allow sufficient natural light and ventilation, not only to individual apartments but also to the common spaces. All apartments have been built with standardized materials and excellent plumbing system with high quality toilet fittings, best quality wooden doors and plastic paint for the walls. Security system has been given special priority and the security measures include: heavily secured gate; security guard, intercom system connecting each apartment with the guard room; stand by generator for uninterrupted power supply; and safety grills for all verandas.</p>
                    <br />
                    <p><h5>SHANCHITA</h5> <img src="./images/sanchita.jpg"/>SHANCHITA is also one of our superb apartment projects, at Hrishikesh Das Road, Laxmibazar.</p>
